<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/587132-how-does-goodreads-pick-their-books-for">How does Goodreads pick their books for the choice awards each year? I have a very eclectic taste and read a lot but there were hardly any books I know on it this year. This one does not even have great reviews. 3.45. Anyone knows?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
